                 </div>\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"647\" height=\"970\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-647x970.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-647x970.webp 647w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-200x300.webp 200w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-768x1151.webp 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-1025x1536.webp 1025w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-1366x2048.webp 1366w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-750x1124.webp 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-1140x1709.webp 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_010-scaled.webp 1708w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The Archetype was wind-tunnel-tested at the Silverstone Sports Engineering Hub, where Bastion says it achieved a six to eight watt drag reduction at 35kmh and 18 to 25 watts at 50kmh when compared to its Superleggera. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-970x647.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-970x646.webp 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-300x200.webp 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-768x512.webp 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-1536x1025.webp 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-750x500.webp 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-1140x760.webp 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-465x310.webp 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-620x413.webp 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/BASTION-ARCHETYPE-HR_016-350x233.webp 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You can fine-tune the Archetype’s design and spec your dream build using Bastion’s bike configurator, which was previously only open to customers who’d already placed a deposit on a bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bastion says it’s only going to build 606 Archetype frames starting from late July. Its order book from existing customers, who were given pre-launch access, is already full until November.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bastion hasn’t quoted prices at the time of writing, but given that the Road Disc frameset cost £12,500 and the complete review bike £19,000 back in 2017, you can guess what to expect.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/newsletters\"><img width=\"970\" height=\"351\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-970x351.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-970x351.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-300x109.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-768x278.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-1536x556.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-2048x741.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-750x271.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-4-1140x412.jpg 1140w\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/bastion-archetype\">Bastion’s new Archetype ‘ultimate road bike’ goes aero plus wide clearance</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Pnorman","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"a7cf14889d92c2477ed69bf7bd2fcf81ef659d5c976ec442d2e92bd42f49d180","category":"Cycling"}